message: Lol. I was a store manager for Starbucks, and depending on the market, baristas start as low as $7.40/hr. They get decent regular hours if they have a good manager. One thing that Starbucks is really good at is marketing to their employees and consumers that Starbucks is a better employer than any other retailer, which is arguable.
